 nekoga,

819
00:55:19,280 --> 00:55:20,040
 dakle,

820
00:55:21,240 --> 00:55:24,080
 ono mi može to dati i vjere

821
00:55:24,080 --> 00:55:25,820
 i ja sam u potrebi,

822
00:55:25,820 --> 00:55:27,060
 dakle, poniznost,

823
00:55:27,060 --> 00:55:30,960
 onoga što mi je potrebno svaki dan

824
00:55:30,960 --> 00:55:34,020
 i pitanje odnosa s drugima.

825
00:55:34,020 --> 00:55:35,720
 Oprosti,

826
00:55:35,720 --> 00:55:37,440
 naoglijeka koju mi opraštamo drugima,

827
00:55:37,440 --> 00:55:39,580
 komunikacija,

828
00:55:39,580 --> 00:55:40,920
 odnosi,

829
00:55:40,920 --> 00:55:43,020
 povređeno strane,

830
00:55:43,020 --> 00:55:45,680
 svijest o tom zlu,

831
00:55:45,680 --> 00:55:46,960
 ok,

832
00:55:46,960 --> 00:55:48,560
 i kako se nosimo s time,

833
00:55:48,560 --> 00:55:52,920
 preporuka Bogu da nas očuva

834
00:55:52,920 --> 00:55:54,400
 od tog zla.

835
00:55:54,400 --> 00:55:55,420
 Tako da,

836
00:55:55,420 --> 00:55:57,980
 tu su onake bazične neke elementi

837
00:55:57,980 --> 00:55:59,400
 tog odnosa s Bogom i s drugima.

838
00:55:59,820 --> 00:56:01,500
 Kad sam malo prije spominjao

839
00:56:01,500 --> 00:56:02,440
 ovu floskulu

840
00:56:02,440 --> 00:56:03,480
 i neke riječke

841
00:56:03,480 --> 00:56:04,440
 koje često ponovljamo,

842
00:56:04,440 --> 00:56:06,680
 ti kad moliš oče naš,

843
00:56:06,680 --> 00:56:08,120
 na koji način ga moliš?

844
00:56:08,120 --> 00:56:09,680
 Da li pokušavaš

845
00:56:09,680 --> 00:56:11,800
 biti prisutan,

846
00:56:11,800 --> 00:56:15,100
 osjetiti svaku riječ

847
00:56:15,100 --> 00:56:15,720
 koju govoriš?

848
00:56:15,720 --> 00:56:17,240
 Pokušavam svjesno,

849
00:56:17,240 --> 00:56:18,000
 pa što ga,

850
00:56:18,000 --> 00:56:19,960
 zbog toga što sam

851
00:56:19,960 --> 00:56:21,200
 profesionalni vjernik

852
00:56:21,200 --> 00:56:22,260
 pod navodnicima

853
00:56:22,260 --> 00:56:25,520
 i izgovaram to često

854
00:56:25,520 --> 00:56:26,780
 i onda pokušavam

855
00:56:26,780 --> 00:56:28,800
 po svijestici,

856
00:56:28,900 --> 00:56:30,580
 odvarem pojedine riječi

857
00:56:30,580 --> 00:56:31,180
 ili sintagme

858
00:56:31,180 --> 00:56:31,920
 koje izgovaram,

859
00:56:31,920 --> 00:56:34,460
 da kako tamo kažu,

860
00:56:34,460 --> 00:56:35,360
 Sveti Franjo je

861
00:56:35,360 --> 00:56:37,080
 počeo jedno molitoče naš

862
00:56:37,080 --> 00:56:38,140
 i ostao je na oče

863
00:56:38,140 --> 00:56:40,800
 zato što je išao u dubinu

864
00:56:40,800 --> 00:56:41,840
 onoga što izgovara.

865
00:56:41,840 --> 00:56:43,460
 Kad bi smo mi tako onda,

866
00:56:43,460 --> 00:56:44,780
 ne bi smo izgovarali

867
00:56:44,780 --> 00:56:46,300
 rečenicu jednu,

868
00:56:46,300 --> 00:56:47,580
 kao i cijelu molitvu,

869
00:56:48,240 --> 00:56:51,020
 ali pokušavam samo posvijesti

870
00:56:51,020 --> 00:56:54,360
 dok izgovaram da koliko je moguće

871
00:56:54,360 --> 00:56:56,740
 budem svjesni onoga što izgovaram

872
00:56:56,740 --> 00:56:59,420
 i podsjecim se na sadržaj

873
00:56:59,420 --> 00:57:00,900
 koji želim izreći.

874
00:57:00,900 --> 00:57:02,900
 Kad pomisliš na Isusa,

875
00:57:02,900 --> 00:57:07,180
 koje ti karakteristike njegove

876
00:57:07,180 --> 00:57:09,680
 budu dominantne

877
00:57:09,680 --> 00:57:11,820
 da ti uskoče u prvi plan?

878
00:57:13,400 --> 00:57:15,320
 Meni je draga sloboda,

879
00:57:15,320 --> 00:57:18,880
 generalno pa onda i kod Isusa

880
00:57:18,880 --> 00:57:22,520
 sloboda spram ljudi

881
00:57:22,520 --> 00:57:23,600
 ili prema ljudima,

882
00:57:23,600 --> 00:57:26,560
 spram normi društvenih,

883
00:57:26,560 --> 00:57:27,560
 religioznih.

884
00:57:27,560 --> 00:57:30,640
 To je nešto što,

885
00:57:30,640 --> 00:57:33,560
 mislim, Isus imao, živio

886
00:57:33,560 --> 00:57:38,160
 i druge poticao da imaju.

887
00:57:38,160 --> 00:57:40,000
 To je nešto što mi je

888
00:57:40,000 --> 00:57:42,260
 jako drago i tu uvijek

889
00:57:42,260 --> 00:57:44,620
 svjestno nesvjesno

890
00:57:44,620 --> 00:57:46,600
 prepoznam te elemente

891
00:57:46,600 --> 00:57:50,600
 i molim, pokušavam ja

892
00:57:50,600 --> 00:57:53,500
 dobiti nešto od te slobode.

893
00:57:53,500 --> 00:57:55,960
 A gdje, u kojim konkretnim primjerima

894
00:57:55,960 --> 00:57:57,540
 vidiš tu slobodu?

895
00:57:57,540 --> 00:58:00,620
 Ma, spram religioznih normi

896
00:58:00,620 --> 00:58:02,460
 je Isus

897
00:58:02,460 --> 00:58:06,600
 duh nas sprem slova, zakona,

898
00:58:06,600 --> 00:58:09,100
 subota koju ne poštuje

899
00:58:09,100 --> 00:58:10,900
 zato što je čovjek važniji

900
00:58:10,900 --> 00:58:13,260
 od tog religioznog principa

901
00:58:13,260 --> 00:58:19,620
 i zakona odnosi s ljudima,

902
00:58:19,620 --> 00:58:25,460
 suosjećanje za marginalizirane,

903
00:58:25,460 --> 00:58:31,920
 otvorenost za drugačije i različite.

904
00:58:31,920 --> 00:58:37,000
 Samar Janac koji je po definiciji nečist,

905
00:58:37,060 --> 00:58:39,420
 zato što nije čisti židov

906
00:58:39,420 --> 00:58:41,780
 njega postaja kao primjer

907
00:58:41,780 --> 00:58:44,020
 primjer konkretne ljubavi.

908
00:58:44,020 --> 00:58:45,820
 Ona sirofeničanka

909
00:58:45,820 --> 00:58:47,640
 s kojom Isus tamo razglaba

910
00:58:47,640 --> 00:58:50,540
 da li joj može

911
00:58:50,540 --> 00:58:53,680
 ozdraviti kćer,

912
00:58:53,680 --> 00:58:55,720
 pa onda razgovara

913
00:58:55,720 --> 00:58:57,480
 i ubiti ona mu pomaže,

914
00:58:57,480 --> 00:58:58,440
 ona koja je poganka,

915
00:58:58,440 --> 00:59:00,020
 njemu da on isto

916
00:59:00,020 --> 00:59:02,260
 raširi horizonte

917
00:59:02,260 --> 00:59:03,000
 i da shvati

918
00:59:03,000 --> 00:59:05,020
 da nije poslan samo židovima,

919
00:59:05,020 --> 00:59:05,780
 nego i

920
00:59:05,780 --> 00:59:07,080
 poganima.

921
00:59:07,080 --> 00:59:09,820
 Tako da,

922
00:59:09,820 --> 00:59:10,200
 evo,

923
00:59:10,200 --> 00:59:14,000
 te nekakve elementi koji...

924
00:59:14,000 --> 00:59:15,160
 Šta osim slobode još?

925
00:59:15,160 --> 00:59:17,980
 Šta ti još spadni na planje?

926
00:59:17,980 --> 00:59:20,000
 Ta osjećaj za čovjeka,

927
00:59:20,000 --> 00:59:20,920
 to je nešto što

928
00:59:20,920 --> 00:59:21,640
 ja sam,

929
00:59:21,640 --> 00:59:24,680
 zahvaljujem Bogu,

930
00:59:24,680 --> 00:59:27,120
 rastao kroz rad s izbjeglicama,

931
00:59:28,020 --> 00:59:29,660
 dakle čovjek u nevolji

932
00:59:29,660 --> 00:59:31,800
 koji je različit drugačiji,

933
00:59:31,800 --> 00:59:35,200
 koji nije lagan,

934
00:59:35,200 --> 00:59:38,320
 nije to ružičasto uopće.

935
00:59:38,320 --> 00:59:40,460
 Kao i sa svakom ranjivom skupinom,

936
00:59:40,460 --> 00:59:42,160
 bili to beskućnici, alkoholičari,

937
00:59:42,160 --> 00:59:43,260
 izbjeglice,

938
00:59:43,260 --> 00:59:45,540
 nasilnici,

939
00:59:45,540 --> 00:59:46,740
 bilo koja ranjiva skupina,

940
00:59:46,740 --> 00:59:50,560
 nije to ni malo ružičast slika

941
00:59:50,560 --> 00:59:52,660
 i vrlo ugodno

942
00:59:52,660 --> 00:59:53,640
 i uvijek lijepo,

943
00:59:53,640 --> 00:59:55,240
 nego je to zahtjevno,

944
00:59:55,240 --> 00:59:58,000
 ima tu i muljanja,

945
00:59:58,020 --> 01:00:00,040
 jer na kraju kada čovjek

946
01:00:00,040 --> 01:00:01,300
 u toj nezavidnoj situaciji

947
01:00:01,300 --> 01:00:04,240
 će napraviti puno toga

948
01:00:04,240 --> 01:00:06,320
 da se izvuče iz te situacije

949
01:00:06,320 --> 01:00:07,340
 i tu smo svi, ja mislim,

950
01:00:07,340 --> 01:00:09,240
 normalni ako se to priznajemo.

951
01:00:09,240 --> 01:00:12,300
 Tako da, ali evo,

952
01:00:12,300 --> 01:00:15,500
 taj rad sa izbjeglicama meni,

953
01:00:15,500 --> 01:00:16,840
 ali gledajući onda,

954
01:00:16,840 --> 01:00:19,960
 temeljeći taj svoj rad,

955
01:00:19,960 --> 01:00:22,360
 sam bio ponukan

956
01:00:22,360 --> 01:00:24,260
 dublje raditi na sebi

957
01:00:24,260 --> 01:00:25,400
 u smislu i u molitvi

958
01:00:25,400 --> 01:00:27,380
 i gledajući Isusa,

959
01:00:27,380 --> 01:00:29,120
 kako se on nosio s time,

960
01:00:29,120 --> 01:00:32,400
 da bih onda imao

961
01:00:32,400 --> 01:00:36,300
 temelj, sigurnost i mir

962
01:00:36,300 --> 01:00:38,560
 u onom radu koji nije bio

963
01:00:38,560 --> 01:00:39,580
 ugodan,

964
01:00:39,580 --> 01:00:41,580
 rad sa izbjeglicama,

965
01:00:41,580 --> 01:00:44,120
 nije bio lagan,

966
01:00:44,120 --> 01:00:45,400
 da bih imao tu sigurnost

967
01:00:45,400 --> 01:00:47,620
 nasprav s svim izazovima,

968
01:00:47,620 --> 01:00:48,480
 preprekama,

969
01:00:49,060 --> 01:00:49,840
 prigovorima,

970
01:00:49,840 --> 01:00:51,040
 problemima,

971
01:00:51,040 --> 01:00:52,220
 da mogu

972
01:00:52,220 --> 01:00:53,880
 čisto srca

973
01:00:53,880 --> 01:00:54,680
 i ono,

974
01:00:54,680 --> 01:00:55,360
 savjesti,

975
01:00:55,360 --> 01:00:56,440
 reći,

976
01:00:56,440 --> 01:00:57,180
 ne, ne, to je

977
01:00:57,180 --> 01:00:58,080
 kršćanstvo

978
01:00:58,080 --> 01:01:00,240
 i to bi smo kao kršćani

979
01:01:00,240 --> 01:01:01,780
 trebali govoriti,

980
01:01:01,780 --> 01:01:02,220
 činiti.

981
01:01:03,720 --> 01:01:05,360
 šta bi, šta bi zapravo

982
01:01:05,360 --> 01:01:06,300
 poručio ljudima

983
01:01:06,300 --> 01:01:08,740
 koji Isusa

984
01:01:08,740 --> 01:01:10,740
 vide samo

985
01:01:10,740 --> 01:01:12,540
 kroz jednu dimenziju,

986
01:01:12,540 --> 01:01:13,400
 blag,

987
01:01:13,400 --> 01:01:14,400
 nježan,

988
01:01:14,400 --> 01:01:15,800
 ponizan

989
01:01:15,800 --> 01:01:17,060
 i tako dalje,

990
01:01:17,860 --> 01:01:20,300
 a sad bi ja volio

991
01:01:20,300 --> 01:01:21,480
 da ga ja i ti možda

992
01:01:21,480 --> 01:01:22,140
 opišemo

993
01:01:22,140 --> 01:01:23,640
 na jedan drugačiji način

994
01:01:23,640 --> 01:01:24,640
 kroz onu priču

995
01:01:24,640 --> 01:01:27,280
 Isusa na tržnici.

996
01:01:27,280 --> 01:01:28,920
 Je li možeš ispričati

997
01:01:28,920 --> 01:01:29,480
 tu priču

998
01:01:29,480 --> 01:01:31,720
 i koju ti to neku

999
01:01:31,720 --> 01:01:32,640
 novu

1000
01:01:32,640 --> 01:01:34,940
 sliku daje o njemu?

1001
01:01:34,940 --> 01:01:36,740
 Isus na tržnici

1002
01:01:36,740 --> 01:01:37,340
 hrama

1003
01:01:37,340 --> 01:01:40,320
 dolazi tamo pred,

1004
01:01:40,320 --> 01:01:41,600
 to je zadnji dan

1005
01:01:41,600 --> 01:01:42,360
 pred smrt,

1006
01:01:42,360 --> 01:01:43,960
 svoju muku

1007
01:01:43,960 --> 01:01:44,880
 i smrtovsku snuče,

1008
01:01:44,880 --> 01:01:46,380
 dolazi i

1009
01:01:46,380 --> 01:01:48,500
 vidi u hramu

1010
01:01:48,500 --> 01:01:50,160
 razio se posao,

1011
01:01:50,160 --> 01:01:50,760
 u smislu,

1012
01:01:50,760 --> 01:01:51,720
 jer na kraju kraja

1013
01:01:51,720 --> 01:01:52,620
 zbog liturgijskih

1014
01:01:52,620 --> 01:01:53,760
 potreba je bilo,

1015
01:01:53,760 --> 01:01:54,240
 dakle,

1016
01:01:54,240 --> 01:01:55,600
 žrtve su se prinosile,

1017
01:01:55,600 --> 01:01:58,980
 šta je bilo,

1018
01:01:58,980 --> 01:02:00,060
 golubovi,

1019
01:02:00,060 --> 01:02:01,580
 janje i tako dalje,

1020
01:02:01,580 --> 01:02:02,640
 dakle,

1021
01:02:02,640 --> 01:02:03,780
 religija,

1022
01:02:03,780 --> 01:02:04,040
 ok,

1023
01:02:04,040 --> 01:02:06,240
 je on konkretan način

1024
01:02:06,240 --> 01:02:08,460
 komunikacije s Bogom

1025
01:02:08,460 --> 01:02:11,680
 i iz praktične razloga

1026
01:02:11,680 --> 01:02:12,680
 tamo je trebalo

1027
01:02:12,680 --> 01:02:13,860
 da ljudi

1028
01:02:13,860 --> 01:02:14,940
 vrlo blizu

1029
01:02:14,940 --> 01:02:15,720
 tog hrama

1030
01:02:15,720 --> 01:02:16,820
 mogu kupiti to,

1031
01:02:16,820 --> 01:02:18,260
 zamijeniti novce,

1032
01:02:18,260 --> 01:02:19,260
 od suda su dolazili,

1033
01:02:19,260 --> 01:02:19,680
 dakle,

1034
01:02:19,680 --> 01:02:21,100
 praktični razlozi,

1035
01:02:21,100 --> 01:02:22,140
 e,

1036
01:02:22,140 --> 01:02:22,940
 Isus upada

1037
01:02:22,940 --> 01:02:23,740
 i,

1038
01:02:23,740 --> 01:02:25,060
 ono,

1039
01:02:25,060 --> 01:02:25,680
 kritizira,

1040
01:02:25,680 --> 01:02:26,160
 kaže,

1041
01:02:26,160 --> 01:02:29,040
 od doma molitve,

1042
01:02:29,040 --> 01:02:29,840
 doma mog oca,

1043
01:02:29,840 --> 01:02:31,660
 ste napravili kuću razbojničku.

1044
01:02:31,660 --> 01:02:32,760
 Dakle,

1045
01:02:32,760 --> 01:02:36,980
 prenamjena onoga što je bilo izvorno,

1046
01:02:36,980 --> 01:02:38,180
 što je vrlo

1047
01:02:38,180 --> 01:02:39,720
 sveto,

1048
01:02:39,720 --> 01:02:40,720
 sveto,

1049
01:02:40,720 --> 01:02:44,420
 ta riječ je jako tu važna,

1050
01:02:44,420 --> 01:02:47,680
 je napravljeno nešto što je suprano tome.

1051
01:02:47,680 --> 01:02:48,800
 Dakle,

1052
01:02:48,800 --> 01:02:50,400
 interesi,

1053
01:02:50,400 --> 01:02:52,140
 trgovina,

1054
01:02:52,140 --> 01:02:53,360
 u negativnom smislu.

1055
01:02:53,360 --> 01:02:56,580
 Kako bi joj karakterizirao to njegovo ponašanje tad?

1056
01:02:56,860 --> 01:03:03,880
 Dokle pravednički gnjev je bio tamo na vidiku,

1057
01:03:03,880 --> 01:03:04,280
 dakle,

1058
01:03:04,280 --> 01:03:05,260
 kažu,

1059
01:03:05,260 --> 01:03:07,320
 uzao je bić i rastjerao,

1060
01:03:07,320 --> 01:03:09,340
 prevrnuo te stolove,

1061
01:03:09,340 --> 01:03:10,680
 rastjerao te trgovce,

1062
01:03:10,680 --> 01:03:12,720
 da bi ukazao,

1063
01:03:12,720 --> 01:03:15,120
 nisu sad tu oni bitni.

1064
01:03:15,120 --> 01:03:18,280
 Bitno je što je napravljeno od tog hrama,

1065
01:03:18,280 --> 01:03:21,640
 što su religijske kaste

1066
01:03:21,640 --> 01:03:24,940
 napravili od hrama,

1067
01:03:24,940 --> 01:03:26,260
 za kojeg su trebali brinuti.

1068
01:03:27,660 --> 01:03:27,880
 Dakle,

1069
01:03:27,880 --> 01:03:28,300
 to je.

1070
01:03:28,300 --> 01:03:31,120
 I onda on nastupa kao

1071
01:03:31,120 --> 01:03:35,060
 pravedni sudac

1072
01:03:35,060 --> 01:03:37,760
 i koji ukazuje ono što nije dobro.

1073
01:03:37,760 --> 01:03:40,840
 A kako bi ti očekivao da će se on ponašat u toj situaciji?

1074
01:03:40,840 --> 01:03:42,880
 Ma, Isus je...

1075
01:03:42,880 --> 01:03:44,920
 Ili kako bi ti riješio tu situaciju?

1076
01:03:44,920 --> 01:03:50,060
 Ne znam, ne znam što je bilo kad je bilo,

1077
01:03:50,060 --> 01:03:52,100
 ali...

1078
01:03:52,100 --> 01:03:55,180
 Da dođeš u crkvu, a neko igra poker, ono na...

1079
01:03:55,180 --> 01:03:56,220
 Ma...

1080
01:03:56,220 --> 01:04:00,440
 Ne, ma treba reći, treba ukazati,

1081
01:04:00,440 --> 01:04:01,740
 treba...

1082
01:04:01,740 --> 01:04:03,480
 Mislim, jučer situacija,

1083
01:04:03,480 --> 01:04:04,560
 u Maksimiru,

1084
01:04:04,560 --> 01:04:06,000
 sjedimo prijateljica i ja,

1085
