 rana,

1341
01:13:20,400 --> 01:13:21,300
 bolesti,

1342
01:13:21,300 --> 01:13:23,340
 patnji,

1343
01:13:23,340 --> 01:13:23,800
 koje su,

1344
01:13:23,800 --> 01:13:25,180
 nisu lagane nositi,

1345
01:13:25,180 --> 01:13:26,240
 pogotovo,

1346
01:13:26,240 --> 01:13:27,240
 možda i nama,

1347
01:13:27,240 --> 01:13:28,760
 lakše nego kad gledamo

1348
01:13:28,760 --> 01:13:29,960
 ljude koji su nam dragi,

1349
01:13:29,960 --> 01:13:30,660
 koje volimo,

1350
01:13:32,640 --> 01:13:33,140
 evo tu,

1351
01:13:33,140 --> 01:13:33,660
 ja mislim,

1352
01:13:33,660 --> 01:13:35,120
 nekakva je sigurnost.

1353
01:13:35,120 --> 01:13:40,700
 Jedan čovjek u mom okruženju je držao govor za svoji 60. rođenja.

1354
01:13:40,700 --> 01:13:46,440
 Pričao je o problemu nekom koji imao u životu.

1355
01:13:48,180 --> 01:13:50,020
 jako veliki problem koji ni mogu riješiti.

1356
01:13:50,020 --> 01:13:51,220
 Godinama ga je mučio.

1357
01:13:51,220 --> 01:13:53,480
 I onda je rekao,

1358
01:13:53,480 --> 01:13:55,420
 da je shvatio,

1359
01:13:55,420 --> 01:13:56,820
 pošto ne može to riješiti,

1360
01:13:56,820 --> 01:13:57,880
 da to zapravo gubi

1361
01:13:57,880 --> 01:14:00,460
 tu definiciju problema,

1362
01:14:00,460 --> 01:14:02,060
 ali problem je nešto što riješavaš.

1363
01:14:03,980 --> 01:14:05,060
 Ako ja to ne mogu riješiti,

1364
01:14:05,060 --> 01:14:05,860
 to više nije problem.

1365
01:14:05,860 --> 01:14:07,800
 Da.

1366
01:14:07,800 --> 01:14:09,460
 Dobra stvar.

1367
01:14:09,460 --> 01:14:11,640
 Ali to je i

1368
01:14:11,640 --> 01:14:14,980
 pomirenje

1369
01:14:14,980 --> 01:14:17,220
 sa činjenicama nekakvim.

1370
01:14:17,220 --> 01:14:20,180
 Da ja više neću imat kose.

1371
01:14:20,180 --> 01:14:22,640
 Da, ne znam,

1372
01:14:22,640 --> 01:14:24,320
 ograničenja koje imamo,

1373
01:14:24,320 --> 01:14:26,860
 da ja neću imat djece.

1374
01:14:26,860 --> 01:14:29,700
 Dakle, ok, to ima odluka, izbor.

1375
01:14:29,700 --> 01:14:31,020
 Žao mi je,

1376
01:14:31,020 --> 01:14:32,980
 ali, ok, tak sam to...

1377
01:14:33,680 --> 01:14:35,800
 da neke stvari

1378
01:14:35,800 --> 01:14:37,580
 tu su ograničenja

1379
01:14:37,580 --> 01:14:40,160
 i kako se nosimo s time,

1380
01:14:40,160 --> 01:14:42,500
 bilo to nešto,

1381
01:14:42,500 --> 01:14:43,880
 izbor naša odluka,

1382
01:14:43,880 --> 01:14:45,660
 bilo to objektivna stvarnost

1383
01:14:45,660 --> 01:14:46,760
 koju ne možemo promijeniti.

1384
01:14:46,760 --> 01:14:50,480
 I, mislim da je zdravije

1385
01:14:50,480 --> 01:14:52,740
 za sve

1386
01:14:52,740 --> 01:14:54,320
 kad bismo se pomirili s time.

1387
01:14:54,320 --> 01:14:57,180
 I tu je sakramenat pomirenja

1388
01:14:57,180 --> 01:14:58,420
 kao neki element

1389
01:14:58,420 --> 01:14:59,660
 u religioznosti,

1390
01:14:59,660 --> 01:15:02,000
 u hršćanstvu, u Kadlečkoj crkvi,

1391
01:15:02,000 --> 01:15:03,380
 nešto što

1392
01:15:03,380 --> 01:15:05,100
 nas potiče na to pomirenje.

1393
01:15:05,100 --> 01:15:06,400
 Sa samim solom, sa drugima,

1394
01:15:06,400 --> 01:15:08,280
 sa Bogom, sa svemirom,

1395
01:15:08,280 --> 01:15:10,200
 sa svijetom oko nas.

1396
01:15:12,200 --> 01:15:14,440
 vjerujem da to sve struke kažu,

1397
01:15:14,440 --> 01:15:16,500
 kad pronađamo mir,

1398
01:15:16,500 --> 01:15:18,300
 oprostimo sebi, drugima,

1399
01:15:18,300 --> 01:15:18,860
 Bogu,

1400
01:15:18,860 --> 01:15:21,020
 da je čovjek radosnije.

1401
01:15:21,020 --> 01:15:22,460
 Da li misliš

1402
01:15:22,460 --> 01:15:24,240
 da je lakše

1403
01:15:24,240 --> 01:15:24,940
 doši do Boga

1404
01:15:24,940 --> 01:15:26,520
 kroz patnju?

1405
01:15:27,900 --> 01:15:29,620
 ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne.

1406
01:15:29,620 --> 01:15:30,340
 Misli, to je...

1407
01:15:30,340 --> 01:15:31,140
 Da li misliš da može

1408
01:15:31,140 --> 01:15:32,000
 neko došli do Boga?

1409
01:15:32,000 --> 01:15:32,420
 A da.

1410
01:15:32,420 --> 01:15:33,880
 Da nije patio nikada?

1411
01:15:33,880 --> 01:15:36,720
 A misli da zavisi...

1412
01:15:36,720 --> 01:15:38,620
 Patnja je

1413
01:15:38,620 --> 01:15:41,900
 ono, normalno dio života.

1414
01:15:42,280 --> 01:15:43,640
 u većoj ili manjoj mjeri.

1415
01:15:43,640 --> 01:15:45,120
 Kad nas boli zub

1416
01:15:45,120 --> 01:15:47,800
 ili kad nam neko umre,

1417
01:15:47,800 --> 01:15:49,000
 to je patnja isto.

1418
01:15:49,000 --> 01:15:50,420
 Ili neki neuspjeh,

1419
01:15:50,420 --> 01:15:51,260
 ili rana nekakva,

1420
01:15:51,260 --> 01:15:53,560
 što je normalno u životu.

1421
01:15:53,560 --> 01:15:55,260
 Tako da, u toj maloj mjeri

1422
01:15:55,260 --> 01:15:57,020
 patnja je normalna.

1423
01:15:57,020 --> 01:16:00,180
 Neki doživjaju veće patnje.

1424
01:16:00,180 --> 01:16:01,940
 Misli da trebamo pripaziti

1425
01:16:01,940 --> 01:16:04,440
 spravo onog klasičnog,

1426
01:16:04,440 --> 01:16:05,640
 tradicionalnog pristupa

1427
01:16:05,640 --> 01:16:08,160
 u Hrvatskoj isto.

1428
01:16:08,160 --> 01:16:11,740
 Patnja je bliža Bogu,

1429
01:16:11,840 --> 01:16:13,260
 križ, križ, križ.

1430
01:16:13,260 --> 01:16:18,240
 Misli da život sasvom nosi križ.

1431
01:16:18,240 --> 01:16:19,400
 Pogotovo ako se trudimo

1432
01:16:19,400 --> 01:16:20,320
 živjeti ispravno,

1433
01:16:20,320 --> 01:16:21,380
 kvalitetno, pravedno,

1434
01:16:21,380 --> 01:16:23,460
 to već ima puno prepreka

1435
01:16:23,460 --> 01:16:24,380
 izazova problema,

1436
01:16:24,380 --> 01:16:25,640
 otpora,

1437
01:16:25,640 --> 01:16:27,080
 toj dobroti,

1438
01:16:27,080 --> 01:16:28,080
 ljubavi,

1439
01:16:28,080 --> 01:16:29,600
 da ne trebamo dozivati

1440
01:16:29,600 --> 01:16:31,040
 neke dodatne neke križeve.

1441
01:16:31,040 --> 01:16:34,240
 A ako nas zadesi,

1442
01:16:34,240 --> 01:16:35,020
 a događa se,

1443
01:16:35,020 --> 01:16:39,020
 nije lagano se nosi s time

1444
01:16:39,020 --> 01:16:41,020
 i mi zavisi smo tu trebali biti

1445
01:16:41,020 --> 01:16:42,700
 puno pažljivi prema ljudima

1446
01:16:42,700 --> 01:16:44,300
 koji imaju,

1447
01:16:44,300 --> 01:16:45,540
 prolaze kar stupatnje,

1448
01:16:45,540 --> 01:16:46,440
 imaju te križeve,

1449
01:16:46,440 --> 01:16:49,540
 puno manje prosuđivati.

1450
01:16:49,540 --> 01:16:52,300
 Ja govorim iz religijskog nekog aspekta,

1451
01:16:52,300 --> 01:16:54,720
 a da, da, to ti je na spasanje,

1452
01:16:54,720 --> 01:16:55,440
 to ti,

1453
01:16:55,440 --> 01:16:58,660
 to je tu,

1454
01:16:58,660 --> 01:17:00,400
 supatiš s Kristom,

1455
01:17:00,460 --> 01:17:02,280
 to je onako, mislim,

1456
01:17:02,280 --> 01:17:04,180
 težak govor

1457
01:17:04,180 --> 01:17:06,280
 i treba ga izreći samo kad smo

1458
01:17:06,280 --> 01:17:08,200
 vrlo bliski toj osobi

1459
01:17:08,200 --> 01:17:10,000
 i kad pripoznamo da osoba

1460
01:17:10,000 --> 01:17:11,080
 to može

1461
01:17:11,080 --> 01:17:13,380
 i tako već sama doživljava to.

1462
01:17:13,380 --> 01:17:14,340
 I onda,

1463
01:17:14,340 --> 01:17:16,000
 joj to,

1464
01:17:16,000 --> 01:17:16,600
 vjeroj mi,

1465
01:17:16,600 --> 01:17:17,480
 može pomoći

1466
01:17:17,480 --> 01:17:19,520
 da se nosi s tom teškom patnju,

1467
01:17:19,520 --> 01:17:20,940
 u smislu muke Kristove,

1468
01:17:21,500 --> 01:17:24,520
 koja je isto ekstremna patnja nekakva,

1469
01:17:24,520 --> 01:17:26,480
 tako da,

1470
01:17:26,480 --> 01:17:28,140
 trebamo biti pažljivi,

1471
01:17:28,140 --> 01:17:28,580
 ja mislim,

1472
01:17:28,580 --> 01:17:30,160
 prema ljudima

1473
01:17:30,160 --> 01:17:32,220
 u patnji koju oni nose.

